Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.88,0:00:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在眼中尚觉遥远的将来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉已经来到面前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并将迅速地成为回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「未来」的表情总是有点不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我们就用笑容去迎接她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 早安啊 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我试穿了制服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很合适哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点高兴而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也成为正式领航员了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 恭喜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级恭喜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就只有这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是说这个的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈要从领航员业界功成身退
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐退的理由不只是那样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈好像很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.37,0:01:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就被邀请担任凤尾舟协会的常务理事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.97,0:01:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅局限于亚利亚公司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.93,0:01:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了整个水上观光业的将来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让她尽一份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 就算艾莉西亚前辈再怎么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法同时兼顾两份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以好像请他们等到我成为正式领航员以后再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到结婚 其实我也吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定也是在等待我的晋级吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我再认真一点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬓子！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听…说艾莉西亚小姐要…要结婚是真的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我这是骗人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从早上开始就有一大堆人打电话来问这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是在哪里听到传闻的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:17.66,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 崭新的开端…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我熟悉工作之前 艾莉西亚前辈都会留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐退仪式全部都由协会来策划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样啦 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级担心你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 蓝华 爱丽丝 谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从知道艾莉西亚前辈要隐退那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就忙这忙那的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都忙得晕头转向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 艾莉西亚前辈总是面带笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都仍旧和平常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间像往常一样流逝着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而又幸福的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个数据是什么来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份文件…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…有份文件我不太明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到处在找你哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人送花来给我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:06:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…都不希望艾莉西亚前辈隐退的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人也是…市民也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家其实都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢艾莉西亚前辈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是水之三大精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是很温柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家的白雪公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想继续跟你在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪停不下来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:07:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实在很久以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里就已经有能力成为正式领航员了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在太害怕失去与灯里在一起的这段美好的时光…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道自己身为前辈必须要振作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须下定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我每次…每次都办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都因为我太任性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多的事情同时发生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这一切又太过幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是非常值得高兴的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论时间或是空间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在不断变化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为自己能够理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但心中却仍旧充满不安与恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并肩走在一起时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉大家走的是同一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实大家都是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在探索着属于自己的路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走在自己的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到AQUA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有大家相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想要与在路的前方的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的未来邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得用笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来送走艾莉西亚前辈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长 今天也要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个预约是庵野波平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来那是邮递员叔叔的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天您不用上班吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？我已经退休啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后就在办公室做管理的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长久以来真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是荞麦茶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的称号是海蓝宝石吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(472,440)\fs20}Aquamarine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到能坐在成为正式领航员的小妹妹的凤尾舟上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔很高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不寂寞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一些交接工作的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈一直都陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…明天的隐退仪式结束以后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就真的变成一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有整个城镇陪着小妹妹你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后透过邮递员叔叔的介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天也有客人预约了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有几位客人是佛洛林咖啡馆的店长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(486,440)\fs20}Caffe Florian
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和钟楼的管理员先生推荐来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在接受很多人的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里的亚利亚公司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开张了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…亚利亚公司…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是骗人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓 你在哭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高兴的眼泪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你成为正式领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到下雪的季节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白雪公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 生奶油可可吗？好久没喝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要多多的奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈 超级任性的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啦 核桃面包久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚刚出炉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满了以前的所有…欢乐的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开这扇门 是我一天中的第一个工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在打开它 平凡的一天就即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这份温馨的光景…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被冷冽的晨风吹散
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将演绎出「现在」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 之后的大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安的说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中邮递员伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近在上班前都会给我送来新鲜的鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说他浮岛的家中开始养鸡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬屋的年轻分店长 蓝华呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近开始有了威信 非常地帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只有我们两个人在的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是跟以前一样是个爱哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说阿鲁前段时间也成功晋级了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 托大家的福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然最近不怎么见面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过蓝华都会把他的近况详细地告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说还长高了一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓先生也成功晋级了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是不知不觉出现在店里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我吓一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我觉得这一定是晓先生特有的关心方式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也到浮岛来玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的跳级正式领航员爱丽丝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是成为周围目光的焦点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而爱丽丝最最热衷的自我原则呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是三个人一块去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不三个人一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界就会毁灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈受到大众的推举
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段时间终于在歌剧院
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召开了一场个人演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然爱丽丝抱怨她怠慢了领航员的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过演唱会当天看到雅典娜前辈那身姿却感动到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷哭了呢 要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬屋的晃前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在名副其实地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为了光芒四射的No.1领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的身姿 真可谓是盛情绽放的蔷薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 她总是碍手碍脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要让我的时代早日到来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.97,0:21:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我知道她心里肯定因为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晃前辈的活跃而高兴得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.48,0:21:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们永远的白雪公主 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙着出席各式各样的演讲和典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集会和联欢会等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都忙得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段时间我还看到了她与祖母一起担任特邀讲师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 在时间允许的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又来看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都像这样 跟祖母一起来看我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有如水之精灵一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我们露出美丽的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被幸福包围着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带来许多开端的风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:23:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果也能送到小爱那里就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.01,0:23:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里前辈 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.54,0:23:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试穿了制服…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.28,0:23:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么样呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 非常好看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.31,0:23:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.57,0:23:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.68,0:24:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点高兴罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:30.94,END,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(445,469)\bord0\shad1\fsp6\3c&H475B5F&\4c&H575757&}愿那起始之风  吹拂到您身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:38.92,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}憶えていますか？ あの日を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:48.91,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ふと感じた ときめきを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:59.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼い日差し浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:03.44,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}風を切る君に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:10.17,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}見とれてると 目が合って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:14.89,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}笑顔こぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:22.01,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}まるで スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:28.95,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an7}鮮やかに 回り出した日々
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:33.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}いつも いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:38.95,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}愛が満ちていた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:43.22,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}きっと スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:52.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あたたかな 毎日を重ねたら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:04:01.36,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}いつの間にか 遠くに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:06.06,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}来ていたのね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:38.92,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可曾记得？ 那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:48.91,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}涌上心头的 感动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:59.04,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴着湛蓝的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:03.44,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎风前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:10.17,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让我陶醉时 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:14.89,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我们齐声欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:22.01,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:28.95,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}炫目光芒中 崭露头角的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:33.31,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}永远地 充满
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:38.95,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让人陶醉的爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:43.22,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}一定如 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:52.94,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}每个温暖的 日子往复着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:04:01.36,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不经意间 从那远方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:06.06,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}来到我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:38.45,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}頬をなでる 優しい風
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:47.62,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}波音に 揺られて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:57.23,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}体の中 ほどけてゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:07.99,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}目を閉じて 見えてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:16.25,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}風の行く道が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:26.35,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}さあ 漕ぎ出そう 光る波へ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:35.51,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}笑顏が すぐ こぼれる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:45.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ねえ 伝えよう このときめき
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:56.27,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}風にのって あなたのもとへ 行くわ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:21:00.47,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ウンディーネ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:31.93,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}風が凪いて 振り返れば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:41.19,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}夕映えに 照らされ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:50.87,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}心までも 染まってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:22:01.91,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}見上げれば 響きだす
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:09.89,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}星たちの歌が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:20.04,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}さあ 漕ぎ出そう 遥か未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.33,0:22:29.06,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}水面に 夢 広がる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:43.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ねえ 見つけよう まだ知らない 宝物を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:49.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}あなたと一緒に 探そう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:54.09,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ウンディーネ
